        "title": "<p>NMJ Lovers | Juliet and Raven</p>",
        "description": "<p>Juliet and Raven's love story is one that has quietly unfolded over a decade. Growing deeper, steadier, and more meaningful with time. </p><p>First crossing paths through mutual friends ten years ago, their connection truly began when Raven reached out and asked Juliet on a date. From that moment, she remembers a feeling that never left. </p><p><em>“I’ve had butterflies ever since,”</em> Juliet shares.</p><p>Over the years, their relationship has evolved alongside them. Through changing seasons of life, shifting interests, and personal growth, one constant has remained. Their commitment to nurturing each other. </p><p>What they’ve built is more than love, it’s a true companionship grounded in understanding and care.</p><p></p><p></p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
