    "d94b5d55-eb15-4cf4-80d0-eaa6ad65a4fc": {
      "type": "content-list",
      "blocks": {
        "template--16177341137065__d94b5d55-eb15-4cf4-80d0-eaa6ad65a4fc-image-3": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "description": "<p><strong>Juliet, what was your reaction when you saw your engagement ring for the first time?</strong></p><p>The moment Raven got on one knee, and I saw that Natalie Marie logo on the top of the ring box, I bawled my eyes out and couldn’t even see the ring through my blurred vision! He knew I wanted something bespoke and designed by him. I absolutely adore my Ceylon Sapphire trilogy. It is truly one of a kind and so special to me. I love that he and the NMJ team spent many months designing it until it was perfect. It is timeless.</p><p><strong>Beyond the physical aesthetics, can you delve into the sentimental value your NMJ pieces hold for you? Are there particular moments or memories attached to them that stand out?</strong></p><p>Beyond its physical beauty, the ring holds deep sentimental value because it represents a moment of certainty and commitment. Every time I look at it, I’m reminded of the thought, love, and intention behind the proposal, as well as the excitement and emotion of that day.</p>",
            "description_mobile": "<p><strong>Charlotte, what was your reaction when you saw your engagement ring for the first time?</strong></p><p>The moment Raven got on one knee, and I saw that Natalie Marie logo on the top of the ring box, I bawled my eyes out and couldn’t even see the ring through my blurred vision! He knew I wanted something bespoke and designed by him. I absolutely adore my Ceylon Sapphire trilogy. It is truly one of a kind and so special to me. I love that he and the NMJ team spent many months designing it until it was perfect. It is timeless.</p><p><strong>Beyond the physical aesthetics, can you delve into the sentimental value your NMJ pieces hold for you? Are there particular moments or memories attached to them that stand out?</strong></p><p>Beyond its physical beauty, the ring holds deep sentimental value because it represents a moment of certainty and commitment. Every time I look at it, I’m reminded of the thought, love, and intention behind the proposal, as well as the excitement and emotion of that day.</p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
